Rules

!! !!Vowel harmony
"Vowel harmony A:а"
%{A%}:а <=> [а|я|\ю у]  [Cns:|ю (у)|ы|и]*  %>: (:Cns) (%{A%}:) _  ;

"Vowel harmony A:o"
%{A%}:о <=> [о|ё]       [Cns:|ю (у)|ы|и]*  %>: (:Cns) (%{A%}:) _  ;

"Vowel harmony A:э"
%{A%}:э <=> [э|е|ү|ө ө] [Cns:|ю (у)|ы|и]*  %>: (:Cns) (%{A%}:) _  ;


"Vowel harmony ӨӨ:аa"
%{Ө%}:а <=> а (Cns) %>: һ ( %{Ө%}: ) _  ;

!!! ы and и
"{I} to ы in Gen case"
